  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/955751cba23f26e88095320eb9392c6f.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=130 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not your typical cozy farm, every moment counts as you and your friends race against the clock to complete chaotic tasks. Can you keep up with the pressure and deliver your orders on time in this high-energy, couch co-op experience? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay and Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/50544e1e91f975e5dfeaf004f8756503.poster.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/50544e1e91f975e5dfeaf004f8756503.webm?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/50544e1e91f975e5dfeaf004f8756503.mp4?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Couch Co-Op or Competitive Chaos</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather up to 4 players and jump into the action. Whether you're working together in co-op mode to plant, harvest, and deliver products or facing off in <strong>Versus mode</strong> to outpace your friends, communication and strategy are key. Every level throws wild challenges your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/bd4a1d5cb0f28fdf901c5e324e780f51.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farming with Power Ups!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance every playthrough with four unique power-ups, making each game more dynamic and exciting. Speed up your plant growth, freeze time, or stun the animals to gain the upper hand</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/c9f865d6de3159d48ecd4246a9e3379e.poster.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/c9f865d6de3159d48ecd4246a9e3379e.webm?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/c9f865d6de3159d48ecd4246a9e3379e.mp4?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting Levels with Tough Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle various obstacles and hazards that test your abilities. Move through tricky levels where managing resources like water and basket space is key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to tackle the ultimate farming challenge? Join us in Crop Chronicles for a fun and frantic co-op adventure that will keep you and your friends busy and entertained for hours.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/955751cba23f26e88095320eb9392c6f.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=130 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not your typical cozy farm, every moment counts as you and your friends race against the clock to complete chaotic tasks. Can you keep up with the pressure and deliver your orders on time in this high-energy, couch co-op experience? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay and Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/50544e1e91f975e5dfeaf004f8756503.poster.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/50544e1e91f975e5dfeaf004f8756503.webm?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/50544e1e91f975e5dfeaf004f8756503.mp4?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Couch Co-Op or Competitive Chaos</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather up to 4 players and jump into the action. Whether you're working together in co-op mode to plant, harvest, and deliver products or facing off in <strong>Versus mode</strong> to outpace your friends, communication and strategy are key. Every level throws wild challenges your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/bd4a1d5cb0f28fdf901c5e324e780f51.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farming with Power Ups!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance every playthrough with four unique power-ups, making each game more dynamic and exciting. Speed up your plant growth, freeze time, or stun the animals to gain the upper hand</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/c9f865d6de3159d48ecd4246a9e3379e.poster.avif?t=1761058296\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/c9f865d6de3159d48ecd4246a9e3379e.webm?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877500/extras/c9f865d6de3159d48ecd4246a9e3379e.mp4?t=1761058296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting Levels with Tough Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle various obstacles and hazards that test your abilities. Move through tricky levels where managing resources like water and basket space is key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to tackle the ultimate farming challenge? Join us in Crop Chronicles for a fun and frantic co-op adventure that will keep you and your friends busy and entertained for hours.</p>",
